        "s21,Movie,Fear City,Sam Hobkinson,\"Various\",United States,2020,TV-MA,90 min,\"Documentaries, Crime TV Shows\",\"A three-part documentary series exploring the rise and fall of New York's Mafia families over decades.\"\n",
